comment: Bass (LAL) firms up as he sets the screen on Gay (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Acy (SAC) cleanly blocks Clarkson's (LAL) layup attempt.
Russell (LAL) commits a take foul on Rondo (SAC).
Bass (LAL) sets the screen on Gay (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bass (LAL) affects Cousins' (SAC) FOM away from the ball as he looks to establish post position.

As Randle (LAL) begins his drive, the on-ball defender Acy (SAC) makes incidental contact that does not affect Randle's RSBQ. Rondo (SAC), the help defender, reaches in and makes contact with the ball while going for a steal.
Cousins (SAC) obtains a legal guarding position prior to the start of Randle's (LAL) upward shooting motion and is firming up as he absorbs the contact.
LHH shows that Williams (LAL) cleanly strips the ball from Rondo (SAC).
Belinelli (SAC) makes incidental contact with Randle (LAL) as he cuts away from the ball.
Acy (SAC) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically as he contests Clarkson's (LAL) driving layup attempt.
RATR shows that Clarkson (LAL) loses control of the ball when Rondo (SAC) reaches in for the steal.
Clarkson (LAL) commits a take foul on Cousins (SAC).
Gay (SAC) legally contests Williams' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
